{"tid":972652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明點解啲人劣評完啲餐廳又唔撚開名","createTime":"2019-01-07T13:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T14:04:31.000Z","uid":80537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"56b001d00ef6edfbbd62423042e527b8d4e3f65a","tid":972652,"uid":80537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"成日見啲劣評野食post<br />\n長篇大論又po曬圖去屌啲餐廳<br />\n但又唔撚開名<br />\n一係就開啲唔開啲<br />\n其實係咩心態？<br />\n你上黎投訴都係想其他人唔好中伏姐或者係同你一齊屌柒佢姐<br />\n但你又唔開名係想點撚樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話你讚完開名就有嫌疑姐<br />\n你彈完又要人估估下係做咩事呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a7b5c9e5b2cf6c75212082c303aebb3c742b78","tid":972652,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"會有機會誹謗"}]}